      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This has been such a reliable ride for me and it's still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. Whether you're zip-lining through your morning commute or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is a total joy to drive. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 28900.0,
