    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Executive Sport Sedan is the ideal blend of sophisticated style and reliable performance. Finished in a timeless Metallic Silver with a smoke-free, perforated black leather interior, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for and primarily garage-kept. The engine delivers a smooth, responsive drive, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. It comes equipped with a high-definition navigation system, heated and ventilated front seats, a premium 12-speaker audio system, and an expansive moonroof. While you may find very minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light highway use, the body is straight and the paint retains a deep, lustrous shine. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently replaced during its last multi-point inspection. This is a turn-key vehicle with a clean title, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 32450.0,
